name: Start Card Transaction Monitoring Requested
type: Conversation/Request
description: Request to start monitoring card transactions for a target merchant and report them into a document.
targetMerchantId:
  type: Text
  description: External merchant identifier to monitor for card transactions.
reportOperationName:
  type: Text
  description: Operation name to call with PayNote/Card Transaction Report payloads.
requestedAt:
  type: Integer # TODO: replace with Timestamp when we can use Date class to format ISO Timestamp in JS expressions
  description: Timestamp (microseconds since epoch) when monitoring was requested.
